You said you met Jeong Hyeon-min once.
Where did you meet him?

518
00:24:53,950 --> 00:24:56,110
Oh, well…

519
00:24:59,700 --> 00:25:00,620
A shop.

520
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:03,370
What shop?

521
00:25:04,120 --> 00:25:07,790
Well, you know where people drink

522
00:25:08,790 --> 00:25:09,920
and sing…

523
00:25:10,710 --> 00:25:12,760
-Ah…
-[woman] Mm.

524
00:25:13,420 --> 00:25:14,880
With guys.

525
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:22,720
[woman] This job can be pretty stressful,
so we sometimes go to relieve our stress.

526
00:25:22,810 --> 00:25:26,520
That night, after a team dinner,
we were deciding where to go.

527
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:29,020
Then Yeong-ok told us to follow her.

528
00:25:31,150 --> 00:25:32,400
[host 1] That's just wrong. Yes.

529
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:34,570
[Ho-yeol] Right, does anyone know him?

530
00:25:35,360 --> 00:25:36,780
Okay.

531
00:25:36,860 --> 00:25:39,870
[host 1] Yes, of course. You're right.

532
00:25:40,620 --> 00:25:42,450
Isn't this Hyeon?

533
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:44,790
-It's Hyeon.
-No, not today.

534
00:25:44,870 --> 00:25:46,670
-Hey, Jjang-gu.
-Yes, okay.

535
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:48,880
-Weren't you close with Hyeon?
-I love you.

536
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:50,630
[host 1] Hyeon? What about him?

537
00:25:50,710 --> 00:25:53,510
We're looking for him,
but it's very hard to reach him.

538
00:25:53,590 --> 00:25:55,800
-He's like that. He's a grasshopper.
-"A grasshopper"?

539
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:59,050
He doesn't work for just one bar.
He freelances here and there.

540
00:26:00,260 --> 00:26:02,850
Do you happen to know her?
Her name is Mun Yeong-ok.

541
00:26:03,970 --> 00:26:04,980
[host 1 inhales deeply]

542
00:26:05,060 --> 00:26:08,560
[background chatter]

543
00:26:09,150 --> 00:26:10,230
Hey, this girl…

544
00:26:11,150 --> 00:26:13,110
She's the one Hyeon tried to con.

545
00:26:14,360 --> 00:26:16,950
She bought him a used car, paid his rent,
and even promised to wait

546
00:26:17,030 --> 00:26:20,620
until he was discharged from the army.
I think she even paid off his prepayment.

547
00:26:20,700 --> 00:26:21,910
[chuckles]
His prepayment.

548
00:26:22,580 --> 00:26:24,830
[host 1] Where does she get all that money
working at a department store?

549
00:26:24,910 --> 00:26:28,330
[host 3] I just don't get why anyone
would do something like that.

550
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:29,830
[Ho-yeol]
Jeong Hyeon-min is a real asshole.

551
00:26:30,790 --> 00:26:32,540
He's not an asshole. He's trash.

552
00:26:32,630 --> 00:26:33,880
Yes, he's trash.

553
00:26:34,800 --> 00:26:35,670
Hey, Jun-ho.

554
00:26:35,760 --> 00:26:38,760
My back hurts so much.
Can we go to a dry sauna first?

555
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:40,720
-There are 22.
-What? Dry saunas?

556
00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:43,010
Host bars in Haeundae.

557
00:26:44,760 --> 00:26:47,770
He freelances, so I'm sure
he's working in one of these bars.

558
00:26:47,850 --> 00:26:49,140
Okay, let's go.

559
00:26:49,230 --> 00:26:50,600
But let's go to a dry sauna first.

560
00:26:50,690 --> 00:26:51,770
[groans]

561
00:26:52,400 --> 00:26:54,820
[Ho-yeol] I'm dead serious.

562
00:26:54,900 --> 00:26:56,480
It really hurts.

563
00:26:57,110 --> 00:26:58,360
What is it?

564
00:26:59,530 --> 00:27:03,740
[light music plays]

565
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:11,170
[Ho-yeol] Gosh, you lost.
Can you help me find…

566
00:27:11,250 --> 00:27:14,540
-[gambler] Let's do this.
-Take a look. Have you seen him?

567
00:27:14,630 --> 00:27:15,750
Take a look.

568
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:17,210
Gosh, I said I don't know him.

569
00:27:17,300 --> 00:27:18,800
VITAMIN DRINKS

570
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:19,970
[Ho-yeol] Hey, wait.

571
00:27:20,050 --> 00:27:22,050
-Before you go--
-I'm busy right now.

572
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:23,550
[waiter] Hello.

573
00:27:25,510 --> 00:27:27,270
Gosh, you're handsome.

574
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:29,180
Me?

575
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:32,980
[light music playing continues]

576
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:37,440
[woman] What do you want?

577
00:27:38,940 --> 00:27:40,030
[Jun-ho] I'm sorry.

578
00:27:47,450 --> 00:27:48,580
[waiter] I really don't know.

579
00:27:48,660 --> 00:27:50,830
-I'm not asking for much. Come on.
-Please, go.

580
00:27:50,910 --> 00:27:52,920
-I know you're tired, so drink this.
-I don't know him.

581
00:28:03,050 --> 00:28:04,260
May I help you?

582
00:28:04,890 --> 00:28:07,970
-Hello, we're with the military police…
-[man] Welcome.

583
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:10,600
-Hey, I'm here.
-[host] Hey, Su-jin.

584
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:14,230
I prepared something nice for you
in room number five.

585
00:28:14,730 --> 00:28:19,030
-Hey, take them to room number five.
-[women giggle]

586
00:28:19,110 --> 00:28:20,360
[woman 1] Are you a host?

587
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:23,070
-No, we're--
-I've never seen you here before.

588
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:25,530
[host] These men are…

589
00:28:25,620 --> 00:28:27,370
[Ho-yeol] You may have heard of us.

590
00:28:28,370 --> 00:28:30,830
-Yes, we're hosts here.
-[women] Oh…

591
00:28:30,910 --> 00:28:32,790
[Ho-yeol] God's gift for room number five
from Gangwon-do.

592
00:28:32,870 --> 00:28:34,170
-[women giggle]
-[chuckles]

593
00:28:34,250 --> 00:28:36,210
-[Ho-yeol] We'll make it worth your while.
-[woman 2] He's so cute.

594
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:38,880
-[woman 3] They're cute.
-[women laugh]

595
00:28:41,380 --> 00:28:44,800
What the heck are we doing?
Do I really have to wear this?

596
00:28:44,880 --> 00:28:46,720
Of course. What else can we do?

597
00:28:46,800 --> 00:28:49,640
Mun Yeong-ok is head over heels
for Jeong Hyeon-min.

598
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:52,020
Do you think she'll gladly guide
two D.P. soldiers

599
00:28:52,100 --> 00:28:56,860
to where her boyfriend is hiding
if we ask her where he is?

600
00:28:56,940 --> 00:28:59,730
You got us in this mess,
so you'd better take responsibility.

601
00:28:59,820 --> 00:29:01,820
Okay. You look pretty.
I'll meet you outside.

602
00:29:02,860 --> 00:29:05,530
[groans]
Seriously…

603
00:29:05,610 --> 00:29:06,780
[Ho-yeol] You punk, just go inside.

604
00:29:06,870 --> 00:29:10,290
-Please just go already.
-No, wait. Wait.

605
00:29:10,370 --> 00:29:12,040
-Aren't you a D.P. soldier?
-I am, but this is wrong.

606
00:29:12,120 --> 00:29:14,790
Mun Yeong-ok is inside.
Don't you want to catch Jeong Hyeon-min?

607
00:29:14,870 --> 00:29:17,580
-We have to, but this isn't right.
-Forget it!

608
00:29:17,670 --> 00:29:18,670
I'm done!

609
00:29:18,750 --> 00:29:21,760
Do you think I want to do this?

610
00:29:21,840 --> 00:29:22,880
Listen, Jun-ho.

611
00:29:23,420 --> 00:29:25,630
-I'm sorry, sir.
-Fuck this. I can't believe…

612
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:26,550
[both yell]

613
00:29:26,630 --> 00:29:27,470
[all cheer]

614
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:29,760
[upbeat music playing on karaoke]

615
00:29:36,770 --> 00:29:37,980
[music stops]

616
00:29:38,060 --> 00:29:40,900
Hello, everyone. I'm Ho-yeol.
I'm as passionate as a tiger.

617
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:43,490
I'm actually here tonight to introduce you

618
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:47,530
to someone new.
[chuckles]

619
00:29:48,700 --> 00:29:50,450
The sorrowful eyes of Yeongwol,
Gangwon-do.

620
00:29:51,030 --> 00:29:52,990
I hope you all brought your swimsuits.

621
00:29:53,080 --> 00:29:56,960
The moment you look into his eyes,
you'll want to dive into them.

622
00:29:57,500 --> 00:29:58,880
Let me introduce him to you.

623
00:29:58,960 --> 00:30:00,210
Let him introduce himself.

624
00:30:01,420 --> 00:30:02,840
[Ho-yeol] Mm-hmm.

625
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:07,090
I want to hear his voice.

626
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:14,850
[feedback]

627
00:30:17,850 --> 00:30:19,230
Hello.

628
00:30:22,570 --> 00:30:23,690
I'm Jun.

629
00:30:23,780 --> 00:30:25,070
-[woman 1] He's Jun.
-[woman 2] He's cute.

630
00:30:25,150 --> 00:30:26,320
[man 1 groans]

631
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:30,030
[sudden music sting]

632
00:30:30,780 --> 00:30:33,870
[women chatter, laugh]

633
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:36,700
[woman 1] I can't drink anymore.

634
00:30:36,790 --> 00:30:38,620
[host] I called a cab for you.

635
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:41,580
Should I drop you off at home?

636
00:30:41,670 --> 00:30:43,800
-[woman 1] You got that right!
-[women cheer]

637
00:30:43,880 --> 00:30:45,300
-[host] Everyone!
-[women] Let's go!

638
00:30:46,590 --> 00:30:47,920
[in English] Next time, babe.

639
00:30:48,470 --> 00:30:49,840
[women laugh, cheer]

640
00:30:49,930 --> 00:30:51,760
[host in Hangul] Let's go.

641
00:30:51,850 --> 00:30:53,510
-Let's go!
-[woman 1] Bye!

642
00:30:53,600 --> 00:30:55,220
-[woman 2] Anyone wanna come over?
-[woman 3] Bye!

643
00:30:55,310 --> 00:30:56,310
[Yeong-ok] Bye.

644
00:30:56,390 --> 00:30:57,600
[women chatter]

645
00:30:57,680 --> 00:31:00,310
[background chatter]

646
00:31:05,230 --> 00:31:06,860
What are you doing after work?

647
00:31:12,820 --> 00:31:14,660
Do you want to grab breakfast?

648
00:31:19,910 --> 00:31:21,080
[cell phone buzzes]

649
00:31:21,170 --> 00:31:25,590
CORPORAL HAN HO-YEOL
I TRUST YOU'LL GET SOMETHING OUT OF HER

650
00:31:34,100 --> 00:31:34,970
What's wrong?

651
00:31:35,050 --> 00:31:35,890
[bottle cap opens]

652
00:31:35,970 --> 00:31:38,020
[Yeong-ok] Did you think
I'd ask you to go to a motel?

653
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:39,430
No.

654
00:31:40,520 --> 00:31:42,350
-That's not it.
-You're cute.

655
00:31:43,770 --> 00:31:45,020
But I have a boyfriend.

656
00:31:46,650 --> 00:31:48,860
[wine pours]

657
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:04,170
You're new, aren't you?

658
00:32:06,170 --> 00:32:08,960
You seem a little lost.

659
00:32:14,890 --> 00:32:16,430
Well, yes.

660
00:32:17,310 --> 00:32:19,470
I work in the same business.
You should come by.

661
00:32:22,560 --> 00:32:25,690
SU-AE

662
00:32:26,440 --> 00:32:27,980
Ask for me.

663
00:32:34,240 --> 00:32:35,660
[sighs]

664
00:32:37,870 --> 00:32:39,080
What's with you?

665
00:32:40,290 --> 00:32:42,370
Why are you looking at me
as if you pity me?

666
00:32:44,540 --> 00:32:45,630
I didn't.

667
00:32:47,420 --> 00:32:48,880
But is something wrong?

668
00:32:53,590 --> 00:32:55,930
You have a shadow over your face

669
00:32:57,260 --> 00:32:59,100
as if you've done something wrong.

670
00:33:03,890 --> 00:33:05,600
[tranquil music plays]

671
00:33:05,690 --> 00:33:06,690
[object thuds softly]

672
00:33:16,070 --> 00:33:17,280
[sighs]

673
00:33:18,660 --> 00:33:19,870
[chuckles]

674
00:33:22,910 --> 00:33:24,460
BEEF RIBS ON RICE, 7,000 WON

675
00:33:24,540 --> 00:33:26,790
Yes, I should eat to survive.

676
00:33:30,130 --> 00:33:32,460
Jun-ho, I ordered rice with beef ribs.

677
00:33:33,050 --> 00:33:34,380
What did Mun Yeong-ok say?

678
00:33:38,430 --> 00:33:40,260
She currently works at a bar.

679
00:33:40,350 --> 00:33:41,390
[Ho-yeol] Okay.

680
00:33:41,470 --> 00:33:43,770
I think she still has feelings
for Jeong Hyeon-min.

681
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:48,650
She lives a tiring life and so do we.

682
00:33:49,310 --> 00:33:51,690
Corporal Han,
why are you so eager to catch him?

683
00:33:53,150 --> 00:33:54,360
It's fun.

684
00:33:55,530 --> 00:33:59,070
Military life can get boring,
but time flies when I do this.

685
00:33:59,990 --> 00:34:01,410
I get to travel the country

686
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:05,580
and carry out the mission
given to me by the military.

687
00:34:05,660 --> 00:34:07,920
You think this is fun?

688
00:34:11,170 --> 00:34:12,750
[scoffs]

689
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:13,920
What's with you?

690
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:17,380
[groans]
Fuck this.

691
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:21,350
Did you just say "Fuck this"?

692
00:34:21,430 --> 00:34:22,310
Hey.

693
00:34:23,350 --> 00:34:25,850
-I'm not hearing things, right?
-[cell phone buzzes]

694
00:34:25,930 --> 00:34:27,980
I guess I've been too easy on you.

695
00:34:28,060 --> 00:34:29,520
I must have done a good job.

696
00:34:29,600 --> 00:34:30,480
Who is it?

697
00:34:30,560 --> 00:34:33,480
MUN YEONG-OK
IF YOU HAVE TIME, CAN YOU HELP ME?

698
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:40,410
Why is he acting like a moody teenager?

699
00:34:40,490 --> 00:34:42,830
[woman] Here's your beef ribs on rice.

700
00:34:51,250 --> 00:34:53,500
Thanks. I wasn't quite sure.

701
00:34:56,340 --> 00:34:57,470
[Jun-ho] About what?

702
00:34:57,550 --> 00:34:59,760
Whether you'd show up or not.

703
00:35:01,510 --> 00:35:03,600
You don't have feelings for me, right?

704
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:05,720
I told you I have a boyfriend.

705
00:35:05,810 --> 00:35:06,890
Where is he?

706
00:35:08,100 --> 00:35:09,350
In the army.

707
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:17,360
[tranquil music playing in the bar]

708
00:35:20,450 --> 00:35:22,200
Ma'am, I'm here.

709
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:23,660
[female owner] Hey, Su-ae.

710
00:35:24,330 --> 00:35:26,240
Is he your new boyfriend?

711
00:35:27,370 --> 00:35:28,370
He's cute.

712
00:35:29,160 --> 00:35:31,500
No, he's just my cousin.

713
00:35:31,580 --> 00:35:33,580
-We're going to have lunch together.
-I see.

714
00:35:34,210 --> 00:35:36,880
I thought you came to ask for money again.

715
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:38,920
Gosh, no.

716
00:35:41,260 --> 00:35:45,470
But while we're on that subject,
can I get paid in advance for this month…

717
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:46,600
[owner] Hey.

718
00:35:47,930 --> 00:35:49,480
What did I tell you last time?

719
00:35:50,060 --> 00:35:52,770
You still need to pay me back
for your outfit and interest.

720
00:35:52,850 --> 00:35:54,690
You're still asking me for that?
It wasn't even that much.

721
00:35:54,770 --> 00:35:56,270
[groans]

722
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:57,440
How annoying.

723
00:35:58,320 --> 00:36:01,240
Are you asking for money
so you can give it to Hyeon-min again?

724
00:36:02,110 --> 00:36:04,490
He always beats you
and asks you for money.

725
00:36:04,570 --> 00:36:06,580
I'm worried about you.

726
00:36:06,660 --> 00:36:08,790
Haven't you come to your senses yet?

727
00:36:09,620 --> 00:36:11,160
Don't talk about him that way.

728
00:36:11,250 --> 00:36:12,710
[glass thuds softly]

729
00:36:12,790 --> 00:36:16,420
If you need cash,
you need to find a different job.

730
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:19,300
And start sleeping with the customers.

731
00:36:20,460 --> 00:36:21,380
What?

732
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:23,340
You don't want that, do you?

733
00:36:23,430 --> 00:36:24,800
[owner scoffs]

734
00:36:27,100 --> 00:36:28,390
Su-ae.

735
00:36:29,520 --> 00:36:33,940
Uncle wants you to come home.
He says he'll lend us the money.

736
00:36:35,650 --> 00:36:36,860
[Jun-ho] He wants us back.

737
00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:39,690
[car horn honks]

738
00:36:39,780 --> 00:36:41,190
What do you think you're doing?

739
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:43,910
I asked you what you're doing.

740
00:36:43,990 --> 00:36:45,530
Why are you…

741
00:36:46,410 --> 00:36:48,530
Why are you doing this?

742
00:36:48,620 --> 00:36:49,700
[Yeong-ok scoffs]

743
00:36:52,500 --> 00:36:53,660
Who do you think you are?

744
00:36:54,790 --> 00:36:56,670
Who are you to ask me that?

745
00:37:02,300 --> 00:37:03,510
You asked me for help.

746
00:37:05,260 --> 00:37:06,590
[Yeong-ok sighs]

747
00:37:08,600 --> 00:37:10,100
And you call this helping me?

748
00:37:15,980 --> 00:37:17,690
I'll do everything I can to help.

749
00:37:20,900 --> 00:37:22,400
[Jun-ho] I'll help.

750
00:37:23,740 --> 00:37:26,240
[Ho-yeol]
Sir, these are beef ribs on rice.

751
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:29,080
We stepped out of line last time.

752
00:37:29,160 --> 00:37:30,450
No, it's okay.

753
00:37:30,530 --> 00:37:33,330
Then why don't we eat? Okay.

754
00:37:33,410 --> 00:37:35,330
-You can eat this later.
-Thank you.

755
00:37:38,420 --> 00:37:40,590
[cell phone buzzes]

756
00:37:43,550 --> 00:37:45,300
[Jun-ho]
I think we can catch Jeong Hyeon-min.

757
00:37:45,380 --> 00:37:46,680
Where the hell are you?

758
00:37:47,550 --> 00:37:50,640
But we need some money.

759
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:53,680
-Trust me on this.
-[sighs]

760
00:37:54,180 --> 00:37:55,480
Give me a minute.

761
00:37:55,560 --> 00:37:57,900
GIFT VOUCHERS, EVENT CERTIFICATE

762
00:37:57,980 --> 00:37:59,480
[woman] Thank you.

763
00:37:59,560 --> 00:38:02,820
[mysterious music plays]

764
00:38:04,530 --> 00:38:06,820
[woman sighs]
What the hell is that?

765
00:38:06,900 --> 00:38:08,860
-[Gyu] Daydreaming again?
-[chuckles]

766
00:38:08,950 --> 00:38:10,620
[cell phone buzzes]

767
00:38:11,530 --> 00:38:14,000
What? Didn't you go back to your unit?

768
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:16,000
[Ho-yeol] Hey, let me borrow some money.

769
00:38:16,080 --> 00:38:18,460
What? Money to do what?

